          "type": "text",
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Sableview Farm is a regenerative and biodynamic farm in the Noosa Hinterland focused on producing premium grass-fed,chemical-free beef while promoting wellness, sustainability, and connection to nature.</p><p>Nestled in the hills of the Noosa Hinterland, our farm is a place where we live slowly, grow intentionally, and stay connected to nature. What started as a personal lifestyle shift has grown into something we now love sharing with others.</p><p>At Sableview, we believe healthy living doesn’t have to be complicated. By getting back to basics, eating seasonally, and living more in tune with the land, we’ve found a way of life that feels grounding, nourishing, and meaningful.</p>",
