            "text": "<p>For us, farming is about more than producing food — it’s about creating healthy soil, healthy animals, and healthy people. </p><p>We spend time with our cattle, handling them in a calm manner and rotationally grazing through our pastures, a calm animal makes for more tender meat. We often say we produce “beef with spirit” because we genuinely care about the entire process, from paddock to plate.</p>",
