          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>For us, chemical-free farming isn’t about trends — it’s about transparency and integrity. </p><p>We believe the quality of food starts in the soil. Healthy soil creates healthy plants, healthy animals, and ultimately healthier people. </p><p>The way food is grown matters, and we want people to feel connected to and confident in what they’re eating. </p><p>This is how we live ourselves, and it’s something we feel incredibly passionate about sharing with others</p>",
